::Ramulus::

Ramulus raises an eyebrow at all the questions thrown at him.

"Um..." he says, getting his thoughts together, "This planet is earth, earth 
in its prehistoric state. If you follow me, I'll give you a tour of the ship, 
and assign you quarters. Although I don't know what Iron Raptor would be busy 
with."

He looks at the bots in front of him. "Would you like seperate quarters or 
one?" He asks, not sure about the relationship between the two.
